channel.title: Ev1l Bunny Server Crasher
channel.description:
Syipkpker client is hardly obtainable these days and people are charging money for it, so I have decided to code my own server crasher far more better than Syipkpker. I will be releasing a server crasher soon. I have been developing it for a few weeks, I do not have that much free time.
[b] Features[/b] -Multi-server crash (May use up a lot of CPU usage) -Names are randomly generated with both letters and numbers, ex. a34grg563 -Nice and easy to use UI -Auto-updated list of popular server IP addresses in the Ev1l Bunny Server Crasher Client -Online/offline checker
I will also set up a website for this crasher, and I will occasionally add updates to the crasher. I will make sure this crasher will [b][u]never[/u][/b] be able to be stopped, I have over twelve years of programming experience, and I know what I am doing. The first version of the crasher will be released in a few hours time or tomorrow. Screen shots will be provided at that time.
-Ev1l Bunny
